songs.title: LA Leakers Outro
songs.lyrics:
[Outro]
Sour milk, just incredible mayne the LA Leakers
We out here mayne rockin with the big homie Kurupt
4/20 the prequel to the street lights
Thank you to everybody mayne for taking the time out to download this joint
Shout out to cashmere agency, shout out to big swab man sawb management
And ah shout out to the whole west coast mayne
Snoop Dogg, Daz, Terrace Martin, Problem, Nipsey Hussle, YB
Dom kennedy, UNI, Bang Loose, Pac div, yo mayne the west ain't goin nowhere
We got so many names I can’t even name em all mayne
But if you repin hip hop and you rep for the west coast
L.A. Leakers mayne we got love for you
Make sure ya check out our website too losangelesleakers.com and you can always catch us
When you’re in LA on the number 1 hiphop station Power 1.06
Yea and make sure you catch up with the homie Kurupt too mayne
Twitter.com/kurupt_gotti, myspace.com/thepentagon or you can find him on facebook mayne that’s kurupt the kingpin and ah
Make sure you go cop that street lights album mayne
It comin out 4/20/2010 mayne that’s uh very shortly
Yeah LA leakers mayne, Kurupt, Young Gotti
What’s up west coast lets go!
